 "lines": [
  {
   "i": 1,
   "en": "Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "Ms. Ozaki, this is..."
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "Ozaki"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "Yes. The audition hall."
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "Idols compete in song and dance,"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "fighting over their futures... A war zone."
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "A war zone..."
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "Uuu, I feel like I'll be crushed."
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "What a huge building..."
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "What the two of us are really worth"
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "is about to be put to the test."
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "If we win, all our work pays off."
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "And if we lose..."
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "Uuu..."
  },
  {
   "i": 15,
   "en": "Eri? You're pale. Are you okay?"
  },
  {
   "i": 16,
   "en": "...Yeah."
  },
  {
   "i": 17,
   "en": "This do-or-die tension is what being"
  },
  {
   "i": 18,
   "en": "a real idol is... Everyday scenery."
  },
  {
   "i": 19,
   "en": "Get used to this air, and soon."
  },
  {
   "i": 20,
   "en": "Now, let's go in."
  },
  {
   "i": 21,
   "en": "So many strangers, all around me..."
  },
  {
   "i": 22,
   "en": "And every one of them is a rival."
  },
  {
   "i": 23,
   "en": "It's almost time, Eri."
  },
  {
   "i": 24,
   "en": "Done with your warm-up"
  },
  {
   "i": 25,
   "en": "and image training?"
  },
  {
   "i": 26,
   "en": "Yeah..."
  },
  {
   "i": 27,
   "en": "There's nothing to fear."
  },
  {
   "i": 28,
   "en": "You did fine in practice, didn't you?"
  },
  {
   "i": 29,
   "en": "I did, but still..."
  },
  {
   "i": 30,
   "en": "You know the one thing you have"
  },
  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "to do on that stage, don't you?"
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "Singing with focus?"
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "Exactly."
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
   "en": "Don't think about anything else."
  },
  {
   "i": 35,
   "en": "Think only of the song."
  },
  {
   "i": 36,
   "en": "Remember that natural calm from when"
  },
  {
   "i": 37,
   "en": "you sang so well the other day, okay?"
  },
  {
   "i": 38,
   "en": "I'll be watching from"
  },
  {
   "i": 39,
   "en": "the audience seats."
  },
  {
   "i": 40,
   "en": "Giving it my all?"
  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "True enough, but don't get abstract"
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "about it. Let's keep it simple."
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "Simple?"
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "Yes. Just think about singing it"
  },
  {
   "i": 45,
   "en": "through to the end. No doubts that way."
  },
  {
   "i": 46,
   "en": "Just singing it through..."
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "Once your head is clear, off you go."
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "I'll be watching from the seats."
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "Beating my rivals?"
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "Don't carry thoughts like that."
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "Right now, they'd only eat at you."
  },
  {
   "i": 52,
   "en": "I'm sorry..."
  },
  {
   "i": 53,
   "en": "Then what should I think?"
  },
  {
   "i": 54,
   "en": "Just think about singing, honestly."
  },
  {
   "i": 55,
   "en": "The enemy isn't your rivals."
  },
  {
   "i": 56,
   "en": "It's your own weakness."
  },
  {
   "i": 57,
   "en": "My own weakness..."
  },
  {
   "i": 58,
   "en": "If I can beat that..."
  },
  {
   "i": 59,
   "en": "The results will follow, guaranteed."
  },
  {
   "i": 60,
   "en": "Now take a deep breath, and go."
  },
  {
   "i": 61,
   "en": "I'll be watching from the seats."
  },
  {
   "i": 62,
   "en": "This audition decides whether I can"
  },
  {
   "i": 63,
   "en": "be an idol out here, in the real world..."
  },
  {
   "i": 64,
   "en": "I have to sing it to the end!"
  },
  {
   "i": 65,
   "en": "No matter how ragged it gets!"
  }
 ]
}